<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id7a5a67c1-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1999—Subsec. (d). <ref href="/us/pl/106/113">Pub. L. 106–113</ref> added subsec. (d).</p>
</note>
</notes>
